        <div class="mb-12">
            <span class="text-label-sm font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.16em] block mb-2">Refund & Payment Policy</span>
            <h1 class="font-display text-headline-lg-mobile md:text-headline-lg text-on-background font-extrabold leading-tight mb-4">Payment rules for the early access batch unlock.</h1>
            <p class="text-body-md md:text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">This page explains payments, refund requests, duplicate payments, chargebacks, and support expectations for the paid batch processing unlock.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Cards List -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
            
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">What you are buying</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">The early access 1-year batch unlock is a paid convenience feature for batch processing Gemini image files and supported Gemini Omni or Veo video files through the browser workflow. The unlock is connected to the Google account email used at checkout and can be checked from the profile page while the subscription is active. It does not give ownership rights in the website, code, brand, Google, Gemini, Veo, Omni, or any third-party content.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Price and currency</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">The launch price is $8 USD or ₹600 INR unless a different price is shown at checkout. The final payment amount, currency, taxes, and provider fees may depend on the payment provider, country, bank, card, wallet, or currency conversion rules.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Payment providers</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">Payments may be processed by Polar, Razorpay, or another checkout provider shown at purchase time. These providers handle sensitive payment credentials. We store payment order status and entitlement records needed to activate or restore the batch unlock.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Refund window</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">You may request a refund within 7 days of purchase if the batch unlock does not activate, if you paid by mistake, or if the supported batch workflow does not work for your compatible files. Contact support with your Google account email, payment provider, payment date, and order or transaction ID.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">When refunds may be declined</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">A refund may be declined if the request is made after the refund window, if the payment cannot be matched to a valid transaction, if the account shows abusive behavior, if there is evidence of repeated misuse, if the unlock was substantially used, if there is a policy or legal violation, or if the request is for an unsupported file type or unsupported video dimension that was already disclosed on the website.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Duplicate payments</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">If you accidentally pay more than once for the same Google account and product, contact support. After verification, the duplicate payment may be refunded or handled through the payment provider where practical.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Chargebacks and reversals</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">If a payment is reversed, refunded, disputed, or charged back, the related batch unlock may be disabled or revoked. If you believe this happened by mistake, contact support with the transaction details.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">No guarantee of perfect output</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">Payment unlocks batch convenience. It does not guarantee perfect watermark cleanup for every image or video. Results depend on source quality, mark placement, browser support, device performance, file dimensions, and other technical limits.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">No rights clearance included</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">Payment does not grant permission to edit, remove marks from, publish, sell, or distribute third-party content. You are responsible for confirming that you own the file or have permission to edit it before using free or paid features.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Access revocation for misuse</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">Batch access may be suspended, disabled, or revoked if a payment is disputed, reversed, fraudulent, abusive, or connected to misuse of the website, violations of the terms, security issues, or unlawful activity.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">Local processing and support limits</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">The normal cleanup workflow is designed to process files locally in your browser. Because files are not normally uploaded to us, support may not be able to inspect your exact file unless you voluntarily share details or samples by email.</p>
        </article>
        
        <article class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/30 bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-on-background mb-3">How to request help</h2>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">Email support with your Google account email, payment provider, transaction or order ID, browser, device, and a short explanation of the issue. Do not send sensitive files unless you understand and accept the risk of sharing them by email.</p>
        </article>
        
